# 🔠 Wordcloud Submission App

A Streamlit-powered web app for collecting participant input via QR code and visualizing it in a custom live word cloud.

## ✨ Features

- 📱 Mobile-friendly submission form
- 🧰 Admin dashboard with real-time word cloud and export tools
- 🎨 Customize colors, fonts, and cloud shape with image masks
- 💾 Download word cloud image and response logs

## 🚀 Run Locally

```bash
git clone https://github.com/AnniMill/wordcloud.git
cd wordcloud
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run submit.py
